939
00:56:03,794 --> 00:56:07,463
They're there waiting
for that moment.

940
00:56:16,606 --> 00:56:20,309
<i>(WINSTON) I did a lot
of those spots with Ali.</i>

941
00:56:20,311 --> 00:56:22,878
He got exposure, being free.

942
00:56:22,880 --> 00:56:27,416
And away from being coached,

