00:57:03,120 --> 00:57:04,887
then he should assume
responsibility of the draft.

956
00:57:04,889 --> 00:57:08,323
<i>(KHALILAH) Somebody would
come out of nowhere...</i>

957
00:57:08,325 --> 00:57:11,927
<i>and say, "You draft-dodger
nigger, go home."</i>

958
00:57:11,929 --> 00:57:13,762
<i>Well, he didn't
like that at all.</i>

959
00:57:13,764 --> 00:57:15,664
I said, "We have to do
this for a living, man."

960
00:57:15,666 --> 00:57:19,268
<i>Don't worry about what people say
about you. You got to keep going."</i>

961
00:57:19,270 --> 00:57:20,702
<i>And then he'd talk
back at me and says,</i>

962
00:57:20,704 --> 00:57:23,972
<i>"You're not out there getting embarrassed.
