964
00:57:26,844 --> 00:57:29,912
I'm not gonna help nobody get
something that Negroes don't have.

965
00:57:29,914 --> 00:57:33,015
If I'm gonna die, I'll die
now right here fighting you.

966
00:57:33,017 --> 00:57:33,782
You my enemy.

967
00:57:33,784 --> 00:57:37,820
My enemy is the white people, not
Vietcong or Chinese or Japanese.

968
00:57:37,822 --> 00:57:40,122
You my opposer when
I want freedom.

969
00:57:40,124 --> 00:57:41,890
You my opposer when
I want justice.

970
00:57:41,892 --> 00:57:43,058
You my opposer when
I want equality.

971
00:57:43,060 --> 00:57:46,795
You won't even stand up for me in
