972
00:57:46,797 --> 00:57:48,330
and you want me to go
somewhere and fight,

973
00:57:48,332 --> 00:57:51,033
but you won't even stand
up for me here at home.

974
00:57:51,035 --> 00:57:53,101
(MURMURING, CHATTERING)

975
00:57:53,103 --> 00:57:57,239
<i>(KHALILAH) The exiled years
was the worst years...</i>

976
00:57:57,241 --> 00:58:00,375
of me and Ali's life.

977
00:58:01,678 --> 00:58:08,083
<i>(ABDUL RAHMAN MUHAMMAD) In Islam we
feel like we're being attacked unjustly.</i>

978
00:58:08,085 --> 00:58:12,988
We feel like there's a
trial period for us,

979
00:58:12,990 --> 00:58:17,793
and if we stand on
righteousness and truth,

980
00:58:17,795 --> 00:58:19,761
God gonna bring us through it.

981
00:58:19,763 --> 00:58:22,564
<i>And that's the way I saw Ali.</i>

982
00:58:22,566 --> 00:58:26,201
I suffered with my brother. He
