00:58:44,487 --> 00:58:46,255
You got to forgive me.

986
00:58:46,257 --> 00:58:50,259
I'm very emotional
when it comes to this.

987
00:58:50,261 --> 00:58:52,861
He paid the price.

988
00:58:55,865 --> 00:58:57,933
(SOBS)

989
00:59:04,541 --> 00:59:07,142
He did what he had to do.

990
00:59:07,977 --> 00:59:10,078
He's the champ.

991
00:59:12,448 --> 00:59:14,983
- (SIREN WAILING)
- (GUNSHOTS)

