00:59:14,985 --> 00:59:17,920
The country was beginning
to pull apart.

993
00:59:17,922 --> 00:59:22,891
<i>(MUWAKKIL) This was a time when the
ideals of rebellion were spreading.</i>

994
00:59:22,893 --> 00:59:28,864
Urban insurrections and violence were
popping out in cities across the country.

995
00:59:28,866 --> 00:59:31,333
<i>(MAN) Violence is a part
of America's culture.</i>

996
00:59:31,335 --> 00:59:34,002
It is as American
as Cherry pie.

997
00:59:34,004 --> 00:59:36,572
America taught the black
people to be violent.

998
00:59:36,574 --> 00:59:41,577
We will use that violence to rid
