00:59:53,123 --> 00:59:54,423
are you with Whitney Young.

1005
00:59:54,425 --> 00:59:57,693
They just go...
(IMITATING KNOCKING)

1006
00:59:57,827 --> 01:00:00,662
There is no need for us to go
anywhere and fight for democracy.

1007
01:00:00,664 --> 01:00:04,933
We working for our liberation, and
it's gonna be in this country.

1008
01:00:04,935 --> 01:00:07,235
And what we gonna say
across this country,

1009
01:00:07,237 --> 01:00:12,174
from Muhammad Ali to a little
black boy in Cardozo High School,

1010
01:00:12,176 --> 01:00:15,510
"Hell, no. We won't go."

1011
01:00:15,512 --> 01:00:17,312
(APPLAUSE, CHEERS)

1012
01:00:17,314 --> 01:00:19,214
(CHANTING) Hell, no!
We won't go!

1013
01:00:19,216 --> 01:00:22,217
<i>(ALI) I'm not here to talk and
say I don't agree with Stokely.</i>

1014
01:00:22,219 --> 01:00:23,085
<i>I don't agree with Rap Brown.</i>

