01:00:28,225 --> 01:00:31,994
One day we all be white, he say. Look
like white people after 200 years.

1018
01:00:31,996 --> 01:00:34,129
One believes that education
and politics will solve it.

1019
01:00:34,131 --> 01:00:37,366
One believes shooting and looting and
burning up the country will solve it.

