01:00:37,368 --> 01:00:38,934
One man believes
integration will solve it.

1021
01:00:38,936 --> 01:00:41,570
And we believe separation, somewhere
to ourselves, will solve it.

1022
01:00:41,572 --> 01:00:45,040
You were quoted as saying on one
occasion, "All whites are devils."

