01:00:47,645 --> 01:00:50,545
that God told him that
all whites are devils.

1025
01:00:50,547 --> 01:00:52,314
Well, God was wrong on
that occasion, wasn't he?

1026
01:00:52,316 --> 01:00:53,649
- You don't...
- I believe every word of it.

1027
01:00:53,651 --> 01:00:55,089
- But you don't actually
believe that all

1028
01:00:55,102 --> 01:00:56,551
- whites are devils.
