01:00:59,023 --> 01:01:00,455
- I mean, I just...
- You said "all," didn't you?

1031
01:01:00,457 --> 01:01:03,992
- Yeah. I'm trying... - I really believe
that all white people are devils.

1032
01:01:03,994 --> 01:01:08,230
I'm not gonna be no phony. I done
gave up $10 million in fighting.

1033
01:01:08,232 --> 01:01:10,165
I'll go to jail
for five years.

1034
01:01:10,167 --> 01:01:14,169
And you think I'm gonna get on this
TV show and deny what I believe?

1035
01:01:14,171 --> 01:01:16,571
- No.
- I believe every bit of it.

1036
01:01:16,573 --> 01:01:17,572
From my point of view,

1037
01:01:17,574 --> 01:01:23,111
what Elijah Muhammad is doing
to you is diseasing your mind.

1038
01:01:23,113 --> 01:01:25,647
And you have the nerve
to be on a TV show...

1039
01:01:25,649 --> 01:01:27,149
and look at me
like I'm wrong...

1040
01:01:27,151 --> 01:01:29,451
for saying, Elijah Muhammad
is poisoning you...

1041
01:01:29,453 --> 01:01:31,420
by telling you that
we're your enemies.

1042
01:01:31,422 --> 01:01:32,521
And I feel it and
see it every day.

1043
01:01:32,523 --> 01:01:35,390
And every black man watching
this show know you our enemies,

1044
01:01:35,392 --> 01:01:37,359
and you have the nerve
to stand up here...

1045
01:01:37,361 --> 01:01:39,327
and say Elijah Muhammad
is poisoning my mind.

1046
01:01:39,329 --> 01:01:42,964
He cannot teach us that you
our enemy. You taught us.

1047
01:01:42,966 --> 01:01:47,102
<i>(KHALILAH) And Ali liked
intimidating you, pissing you off.</i>

1048
01:01:47,104 --> 01:01:50,138
<i>He loved that. That's
his comfort zone.</i>

1049
01:01:50,140 --> 01:01:52,174
And when you're in
your comfort zone,

1050
01:01:52,176 --> 01:01:54,576
nobody in the world
can penetrate you,

1051
01:01:54,578 --> 01:01:56,378
and you can be who
you wanna be.

1052
01:01:56,380 --> 01:02:00,182
I'd like to start off by
saying, <i> As-salaam alaikum.</i>

1053
01:02:00,184 --> 01:02:02,651
(ALL)
<i>Wa alaikum.</i>

