01:02:09,493 --> 01:02:12,928
<i>he was a much more
attractive character.</i>

1058
01:02:12,930 --> 01:02:15,330
<i>(ALI) And once you
find out who you are,</i>

1059
01:02:15,332 --> 01:02:19,101
then you're start saying,
