1067
01:02:47,498 --> 01:02:51,066
- (WOMAN) Yeah! - (APPLAUSE)

1068
01:02:51,068 --> 01:02:54,569
I have gained a
peace of heart.

1069
01:02:54,571 --> 01:02:57,773
I now know that
I'm in content...

1070
01:02:57,775 --> 01:03:01,643
with Almighty God himself.

1071
01:03:01,744 --> 01:03:04,780
(Martin Luther King, Jr.) And
there are those who are seeking...

1072
01:03:04,782 --> 01:03:10,118
to equate dissent
with disloyalty.

1073
01:03:10,120 --> 01:03:12,287
It is my hope...

1074
01:03:12,289 --> 01:03:15,357
that every young man
in this country...

1075
01:03:15,359 --> 01:03:21,763
who finds this war objectionable
and abominable and unjust...

1076
01:03:21,765 --> 01:03:25,767
would file as a
conscientious objector.

1077
01:03:25,769 --> 01:03:29,104
And no matter
what you think...

1078
01:03:29,106 --> 01:03:33,542
of Mr. Muhammad Ali's religion,

1079
01:03:33,544 --> 01:03:39,347
you certainly have to
admire his courage.

1080
01:03:51,627 --> 01:03:55,831
<i>(ALI) Our great leaders like
