01:28:22,831 --> 01:28:26,533
<i>it should have
been Muhammad Ali.</i>

1517
01:28:26,535 --> 01:28:28,568
<i>(LIPSYTE)</i>
<i>In the '60s and '70s,</i>

1518
01:28:28,570 --> 01:28:33,674
<i>he was the most recognizable
face in the world.</i>

1519
01:28:33,676 --> 01:28:36,810
We created a symbol.

1520
01:28:37,211 --> 01:28:43,550
<i>Muhammad Ali has long
since been supplanted...</i>

1521
01:28:43,552 --> 01:28:47,621
<i>by what we believe he is.</i>

1522
01:28:47,623 --> 01:28:50,157
One more time! Who's the
champ of the world?

1523
01:28:50,159 --> 01:28:51,091
(AUDIENCE)
Muhammad Ali!

1524
01:28:51,093 --> 01:28:54,161
<i>(LIPSYTE) There are so many
ways of looking at him...</i>

1525
01:28:54,163 --> 01:28:57,297
<i>that have only
to do with us...</i>

1526
01:28:57,299 --> 01:29:02,069
<i>and have nothing
to do with him.</i>

1527
01:29:02,870 --> 01:29:07,574
When Muhammad Ali
took that stand...

1528
01:29:08,976 --> 01:29:12,279
- That was a hell of a stand.
- It certainly was.

1529
01:29:12,281 --> 01:29:15,649
<i>(HANA) And my father was
always more than a boxer.</i>

1530
01:29:15,651 --> 01:29:17,951
To me, he's the eighth
wonder of the world.

1531
01:29:17,953 --> 01:29:19,219
That's the one title
I'm waiting for.

1532
01:29:19,221 --> 01:29:23,190
Muhammad Ali... the eighth
wonder of the world.

1533
01:29:27,595 --> 01:29:30,197
<i>(RAHAMAN)</i>
<i>I love you, champ.</i>

1534
01:29:30,199 --> 01:29:31,832
You're my soul and my heart.

1535
01:29:31,834 --> 01:29:34,101
Only brother I got. Love you.

1536
01:29:36,003 --> 01:29:38,038
I love you. Peace.

